<item>
            <title>[KAFKA-13927] Kafka Connect Sink Connector Success after RetriableException, no commit offset to remote.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-13927</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I made a custom SinkConnector.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;and I set retries with RetriableException.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In normal case, successfully offset commited with no LAG.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;but one or more RetriableException occured and then, retry make success&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;there are LAG about sucess record, despite the retry success.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
